Instructions to Unzip and Import the Dump File
 
1. Download the File:
   Download the res_toxval_v95.dmp.gz file from the provided URL.
 
2. Unzip the File:
   Open Command Prompt or Terminal.
   Navigate to the directory where the file is downloaded.
   Run the following command to unzip:
   gunzip res_toxval_v95.dmp.gz
 
3. Import the Database:
   Run the following command to import the database:
   mysql -u [username] -p res_toxval_v95 < res_toxval_v95.dmp
   Replace [username] with your MySQL username.
   Enter your MySQL password when prompted.